The LLC Laptop Loan Policy of George Brown College has undergone changes as of December 18, 2023. The policy-related information can be found on Library News & Services. The contact details for the LLC are:

Address: Building H, 3rd Floor, Room 367, 341 King Street East, Toronto ON M5A 1L1, Canada
Phone number: 416-415-5000 ext. 4950 (local) or 1-877-515-5559 (TTY)
Email: ask.george@georgebrown.ca
Website: Visit Our Social Media Hub

The nearest subway station is King. The phone numbers and email are for inquiries related to the LLC specifically. It's important to note that the information contained on the website may change without notice, and students should verify George Brown College fee requirements.
